headline: FS KKR Capital Corp. Announces Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Results; Declares First Quarter 2025 Distribution of $0.70 per share
summary: FS KKR Capital Corp. (NYSE: FSK), or the Company, today announced its financial and operating results for the quarter and year ended December 31, 2024, and that its board of directors has declared a first quarter 2025 distribution of $0.70 per share.
